	Allegheny Insurance Services 	































































 







 




 







































 


 




Home
kchannels


Don’t Compromise
Don’t compromise protection for a quick-click online insurance policy. We don’t believe anyone should have to fit their insurance needs into a one-size-fits-all mold. Whether your business, family, or dreams are large or small, your needs are unique. We examine these needs on a client-by-client basis and develop a risk management program that addresses your needs and yours alone.
As an independent insurance agency, we can comparatively shop your insurance coverage among the quality insurance carriers we represent. We find you the best insurance value. We follow the sale with prompt and personal service.


Commercial InsuranceWe offer customized Commercial Insurance designed to address risks that are unique to your business, large or small.Learn More
Life, Health & BenefitsAllegheny Insurance can help take the worry out of selecting health or life insurance coverage for you and your family.Learn More
Personal InsuranceFamilies come in all shapes and sizes… Whatever the differences, each has one thing in common… the need for adequate insurance.Learn More

Our Preferred Carriers
Allegheny Insurance is an independent insurance agency that represents many insurance companies. Our companies provide outstanding claims service, offer outstanding customer and agency policy service, offer competitive products and rates and are considered innovative leaders in the industry.










