Company Overview of Alleghany Insurance Holdings LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Alleghany Insurance Holdings LLC is a holding company, which through its subsidiaries, offers property and casualty insurance services. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is based in New York, New York. Alleghany Insurance Holdings LLC operates as a subsidiary of Alleghany Corporation.


375 Park AvenueSuite 3201New York, NY 10152-0002United StatesFounded in 1999



Phone: 212-752-1356

Fax: 212-759-8149








