Customized small business insuranceHiscox offers professional services businesses a new way to buy small business insurance either online or over the phone from a licensed agent in minutes. This means we can offer customized small business insurance quotes and coverage at very competitive premiums. Small business insurance quotesAll of our products can be bought online or over the phone by calling one of our licensed advisors. To see example insurance rates, simply click on the links below or start a quote now.Professional Liability insurance quote – coverage from $22.50 a monthProfessional liability insurance, also called errors and omissions insurance (E & O insurance), protects your business if you are sued for negligently performing your services, even if you haven’t made a mistake.Errors and Omissions insurance quote – coverage from $22.50 a monthYou should seriously consider errors and omissions coverage if your business:Provides a professional serviceRegularly gives adviceIs required by its clients to have E&O insurance General Liability insurance quote – coverage from $29.17 a monthGeneral liability insurance protects your business from another person or business’s claims of bodily injury, associated medical costs, and damage to property.Business owner insurance quote - coverage from $41.67 a month  Reduce your insurance premiumsWe offer various ways you can reduce your insurance costs.Deductibles – We recognize that you are taking on more of the risk when you choose a higher  deductible and we reward this by offering lower premiums.Risk management rewards – By utilizing good risk management practices you are proactively lowering your risk and we reward you by offering lower small business insurance rates.Switcher discounts – If you currently have small business insurance with another company we offer up to a 15% rate reduction when you buy direct from us.Multiple product discount – If you purchase more than one product direct from us we will offer up to a 5% rate deduction. Customized small business insurance As small business insurance specialists we understand that every business is different, that is why we don’t offer a one-size-fits-all-solution. We customize our policies to the specific risks you face, ensuring you get the right coverage at the right price.Get a fast, free quote now and get that Hiscox confidence behind your business, too. If you prefer, you can call us at 1-866-283-7545 and speak with a Hiscox licensed agent, Monday thru Friday from 8am-10pm ET.  











  






